AB  - Patients with cardiovascular disease (CVD) often encounter challenges in establishing and maintaining heart-healthy physical activity habits, even after successfully completing a cardiac rehabilitation program. Digital health technologies hold promise to support long-term habit formation in the secondary prevention of CVD. The aktivplan digital health intervention has been developed to support patients with CVD in establishing long-term heart-healthy physical activity habits.
