AB  - In physical reality, mobility limitations often hinder the ability of older individuals to fully interact with the world. Aging increases the likelihood of a decline in social activities. New technologies, including immersion technologies, are increasingly gaining attention as society grapples with the challenges of an aging population. The metaverse offers a compelling opportunity to reimagine the perspective of empowering older individuals.
