AB  - In the management of bipolar disorder, the search for appropriate non-pharmacological interventions as adjuncts to pharmacotherapy is underway. Various lifestyle interventions focusing on relaxation contribute to mood stabilization. However, the specific needs and preferences of individuals with bipolar disorder concerning relaxation interventions remain unexplored.
